prodNameC: 免疫特 抗甲狀腺球蛋白抗體試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Anti-TG Ab Test Units (LTG1)：Each barcode-labeled unit contains one bead coated with highly purified thyroglobulin.
Anti-TG Ab Reagent Wedges(LTGA,LTGB)：LTGA：6.5 mL buffer matrix.
                                      LTGB：6.5 mL alkaline phosphate(bovine calf intestine)conjugated to a monoclonal murine anti-human IgG antibody in buffer.
Anti-TG Ab Adjustors(LTGL,LTGH)：Two vials(Low and High), of lyophilized TG autoantibodies in a human serum/buffer matrix.
Thyroid Autoantibody Sample Diluent(LAAZ4)：For the manual dilution of patient sample.100 mL anti-TG/anti-TPO antibody-free buffer matrix.
applicantAddr: 台北市南港區園區街３號８樓
efficacy: 定量檢測人體血清、EDTA血漿和肝素化血漿中的甲狀腺球蛋白(TG)自體抗體。
